# Git: preview vs production

For **`grace.ai`** and **`ahackaday-site`** (when working in those repos):

- **Default push target:** branch **`mono`** — gives Vercel/GitHub preview before production.
- **Push to `main` only** when the user explicitly asks to deploy / ship to production / merge to prod.

Workflow: commit on `mono` (or checkout `mono`, merge work, push `origin mono`). Production merges: `mono` → `main` when ready.
